%h2 File stat

%ul
  %li
    ID of device containing file:
    = @stat_buf.st_dev
    (devices numbers list:
    %a{href: "https://www.kernel.org/doc/Documentation/admin-guide/devices.txt"} devices.txt
    )
  %li
    Inode number:
    = @stat_buf.st_ino
  %li
    File type and mode:
    = @stat_buf.st_mode
  %li
    Number of hard links:
    = @stat_buf.st_nlink
  %li
    User ID of owner:
    = @stat_buf.st_uid
  %li
    Group ID of owner:
    = @stat_buf.st_gid
  %li
    Device ID (if special file):
    = @stat_buf.st_rdev
  %li
    Total size in bytes
    = @stat_buf.st_size
  %li
    Block size for filesystem I/O:
    = @stat_buf.st_blksize
  %li
    Number of 512 B blocks allocated:
    = @stat_buf.st_blocks
  %li
    Time of last access:
    = @stat_buf.st_atime
  %li
    Time of last modification:
    = @stat_buf.st_mtime
  %li
    Time of last status change:
    = @stat_buf.st_ctime
